---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---
<section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-[#0B0C10] relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Fundo Decorativo Estilo Blueprint -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#ffffff 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative">
    
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
      <span class="font-label text-[#004E98] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-xs mb-4 block">Processo de Engenharia Digital</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-white">
        A Jornada da Economia: <br class="hidden md:block"/> <span class="text-[#FBB03B]">Como funciona na prática?</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#004E98] mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Blueprint Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-0 border border-white/10 rounded-sm">
      
      <!-- Passo 1 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 border-b lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-white/10 relative group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
        <!-- Numeral Ajustado (Mais visível e amarelo no hover) -->
        <span class="absolute top-4 md:top-6 right-6 md:right-8 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-black text-white/20 group-hover:text-[#FBB03B] transition-all duration-500">01</span>
        
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 border border-[#004E98]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-10 group-hover:border-[#004E98] transition-colors shadow-lg">
            <Icon name="chat_bubble" class="text-3xl md:text-5xl text-[#004E98]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white uppercase tracking-widest">O Alinhamento</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-[240px]">
            Você entra em contato, me conta sua ideia e eu analiso as medidas do seu ambiente para entender a complexidade do projeto.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Passo 2 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 border-b lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-white/10 relative group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
        <span class="absolute top-4 md:top-6 right-6 md:right-8 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-black text-white/20 group-hover:text-[#FBB03B] transition-all duration-500">02</span>
        
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 border border-[#004E98]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-10 group-hover:border-[#004E98] transition-colors shadow-lg">
            <Icon name="architecture" class="text-3xl md:text-5xl text-[#004E98]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white uppercase tracking-widest">O Planejamento 3D</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-[240px]">
            Crio o projeto visual em 3D e todo o detalhamento executivo oculto. Você aprova o design e eu gero a lista exata de materiais sem desperdícios.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Passo 3 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 border-b md:border-b-0 lg:border-r border-white/10 relative group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
        <span class="absolute top-4 md:top-6 right-6 md:right-8 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-black text-white/20 group-hover:text-[#FBB03B] transition-all duration-500">03</span>
        
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 border border-[#004E98]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-10 group-hover:border-[#004E98] transition-colors shadow-lg">
            <Icon name="factory" class="text-3xl md:text-5xl text-[#004E98]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white uppercase tracking-widest">A Compra Direta</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-[240px]">
            Eu envio o plano de corte diretamente para a fábrica (via Cortecloud). Você paga o valor real do material e da usinagem, direto para a central.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Passo 4 -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10 relative group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
        <span class="absolute top-4 md:top-6 right-6 md:right-8 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-black text-white/20 group-hover:text-[#FBB03B] transition-all duration-500">04</span>
        
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 border border-[#004E98]/40 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 md:mb-10 group-hover:border-[#004E98] transition-colors shadow-lg">
            <Icon name="construction" class="text-3xl md:text-5xl text-[#004E98]" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-headline text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-3 md:mb-4 text-white uppercase tracking-widest">A Montagem</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-[240px]">
            O material chega pronto na sua casa. Você contrata o montador, e eu entrego a ele o Dossiê de Execução e suporte total.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
